thread.title: Breanna Fikes
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Breanna Fikes

author: Breanna Fikes
title: Breanna Fikes
text: The staff was helpful in making sure I had the right size unit for the amount and type of stuff that I would be storing. I purchased a $20 lock in which one of the keys broke off into it after their business hours, but she still helped me get it out and told me to come back the next day so that she could replace it.
